'''Mablung''' means "Heavy Hand" in [[Sindarin]] (from ''[[mab]]-'', "hand" and ''[[long]]'', "heavy"), and can refer to:
* '''[[Mablung]] (died {{FA|503}}), an [[Sindar|Elven]] captain of [[Doriath]] killed during a [[battle in the Thousand Caves]].'''
* [[Mablung (ranger of Ithilien)]] (fl. {{TA|3019}}), a [[Rangers of Ithilien|Ranger of Ithilien]] during the [[War of the Ring]].
